Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去清洁肚脐眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.11,0:01:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗那家伙  还是那么受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈是未婚妻所以没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望着梨斗的西连寺春菜的那个眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么看都是恋爱中的眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来  天条院学姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个“哼”也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古手川唯的那个盯着他的眼神也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都像是喜欢梨斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有金色闇影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计…也是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且  梨斗那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹美柑也很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被好女孩围着  不就像江户城的大奥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}大奥：江户城内将军夫人的府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:03:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗大人驾到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗大人  梨斗大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈  不客气不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也要成为江户城的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？我变成江户城的大人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大奥  大奥在哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大奥在哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说江户城的大人措辞要高雅点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大奥在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大奥在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大奥在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:03:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大奥在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大奥在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山大人驾到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  这里就是日本后宫  嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山大人  请宠幸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请宠幸我吧  也请宠幸我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是梦啊  噩梦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1500)}噩梦啊！快醒过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个噩梦啊…噩梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是噩梦  快醒过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噩梦…噩梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个噩梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳命来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  西连寺春菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险  危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没礼貌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没礼貌的家伙是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛学姐  还有绫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是凛学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是绫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是凛助三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绫格之进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小助  还有小格  那么这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真是天条院沙姬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么天条院沙姬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你知道在这里的是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伟大的前副将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天条院沙姬光国公是也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}注：德川光国，日本水户藩第二代藩主，德川家康的孙子。\N编纂《大日本史》，后任中纳言，称水户黄门。\N前面提到的助三郎和格之进曾协助光国编纂《大日本史》。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天条院沙姬光国公？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是水户黄门嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小格  刚才讲那些话不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  没看到这个家徽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头抬得太高  低下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小格  印盒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…哎  没了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这种地方脱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小助  你没拿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…应该没拿  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们脑子里在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许在大人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛助  绫格  你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷  要感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:06:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  你们居然在江户城中心做这么无耻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扰乱江户风纪的怪家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  古手川唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么“啊  古手川唯”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花花公子唯就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花花公子唯…远山唯四郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}注：此名出自远山金四郎，同为江户时代人物。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北町奉行  远山唯四郎大人  上座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}注：北町为地名，奉行相当于县令一类职务。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此人扰乱江户风纪之事  已水落石出  实属不当
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有扰乱江户的风纪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使能蒙蔽世人的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:08:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也瞒不过我远山樱的睿目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三叶草的家徽？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个印盒  难道是天条院沙姬黄门大人的印盒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么奉行大人会有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时  暂时…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何  请您保密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  金色闇影  不对…是钱形金色闇次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}注：恶搞野村胡堂的侦探故事《钱行平次捕物账》主人公钱行平次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远山唯即远山唯四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盗取天条院沙姬黄门大人的印盒之罪  由我来惩戒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你能否接住我钱形金色闇次的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么打到我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？这个声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿呀  嘿呀  着火啦  着火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾和吵架是江户的精华
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么  很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那里的老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火已经灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？好快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人别一直愣在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快站起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  一…二…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好  好好好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吉利啊  别了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变了个角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是传七捕物帐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}注：来自冈本绮堂的半七捕物帐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一身轻  仇已报  死而无憾矣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽身将死  吾已心满意足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色闇影的忠臣藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来做什么的根本不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么来着  不是优胜者游行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花魁的盛装游行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  你弄成这个样子干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎…萨斯丁也变这样了  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于  终于从噩梦中醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  我刚做噩梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发明的呼呼晚安君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼呼晚安君？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛学姐  还有绫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是凛学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是绫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是凛助三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绫格之进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这位就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真是天条院沙姬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么天条院沙姬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你知道在这里的是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伟大的的前副将军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天条院沙姬光国公是也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小格  刚才讲那些话不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  没看到这个家徽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小格  印盒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…哎  没了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了别脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小助  你没拿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…应该没拿  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许在大人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这里脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛助  绫格  你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷  要感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  你们居然在江户城中心做这么无耻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了不是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扰乱江户风纪的怪家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  古手川…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么“所以说  古手川”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花花公子唯就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才已经听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北町奉行  远山唯四郎大人  上座
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？不是法庭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像跳过去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿呀  嘿呀  着火啦  着火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾和吵架是江户的精华
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳过头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇   又是萨斯丁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎么醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据上述情况  审问结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判处此人  斩首示众
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩首示众？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是这副打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来  这个事件就告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  前面是画板  看上去像透明的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:15:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  还以为我死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又来了  闇影忠臣藏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是温温的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阁下是吉良上野介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是不是  搞错了搞错了搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到吉良大人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  出来  出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  吉良大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被误认为是吉良上野介  被赤穗浪士追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}注：吉良义央，官位4品，封上野介，也被称为吉良上野介。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出船啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我也上船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽田未央是艄公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山大人  请宠幸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈理沙的茶摊儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋啊  武士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子坐在我的店前面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却一杯茶也不要  这样怎么做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦  多谢多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来吃点团子怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我也要了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屡次关照  多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屡次关照？我今天是第一次来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个能言善道的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山大人  请宠幸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驿站大街吗  好想去旅店洗个澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这打扮简直就像个罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方有女性的和服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就借它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不要遇到钱形金色闇次  或者远山唯四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有赤穗浪士这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  很危险的  睁大眼睛走路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不会是越田姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是不是  我不是越田姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御门老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是御门老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃受大姐恩惠的  原来穿兜裆布的御门驹形茂平是也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}注：驹形茂兵卫，江户时代落魄的相扑力士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驹形茂平？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太专业了不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了吗  大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然成了无所作为的世俗之人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我茂平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让十年前  给我簪子  钱袋  还有意见的大姐赏脸一看的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我驹形的一本刀土俵入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}注：一本刀土俵入是有驹形茂兵卫登场的时代剧剧本名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么住在这里的人脱的这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿呀  嘿呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…  这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足柄山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美柑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美柑金太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}注：金太郎，源赖光四天王之一。阪田金时幼名，怪童，力大无比。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  变成熊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨在熊身上练习马术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是时代剧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下来是相扑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别呀  很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让美柑受伤的话我会挨梨斗骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是菈菈岛太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  都是古代物语系列啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是乌龟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龟？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被孩子们欺负的时候我救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为回礼就带我进龙宫城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往龙宫城  GOGOGO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是龙宫城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会有性感的龙宫仙女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山大人  请宠幸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜  恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七…七福神？还全是菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个头脑简单的家伙  怎么处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是头脑简单的家伙  我是猿山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个头脑简单的家伙  就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户第一的鱼贩子  菈菈心太助
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又回到时代剧系列了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了  这种事情怎么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要把我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么处理  我可江户的鱼贩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把你做成生鱼片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生鱼片？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献给大奥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山大人生鱼片  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山大人的生鱼片大人  请宠幸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请宠幸我吧  请宠幸我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快快  很新鲜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1400)}不要吃我  我不好吃的  别吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很难吃  我很难吃的  别吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿  猿山？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  猿山坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1400)}不要  我很难吃的  不要  真的很难吃 …
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和我两个人单独说话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你最近有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？我  很怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很怪啊  比如说今天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.55,0:23:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  请忘记那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我一时丧失理智
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个样子钻进梨斗的被窝里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:24:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  好丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你这反应就和以前完全不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  To  LOVEる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.64,0:24:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点小害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是发生什么可怕的事的征兆吧

